  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">National Youth Policy Review</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">A new and more improved youth policy document. This improved document will help to create equal opportunities for men and women and the youth who are victims of social exclusion. The new document will help to put the issues of the issue of the front burner of national policy and development discussions so that critical issues such as skills development will receive the needed attention to ultimately help reduce unemployment and poverty among the youth</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&#x2022;	Critical review of the existing Policy to identify gaps as well as what challenges will be required to align a Youth Policy to the current youth development aspirations of Ghana
&#x2022;	This will be achieved through broader Stakeholder consultations that is genuinely inclusive.
&#x2022;	Memos and position papers from key experts will be invited
&#x2022;	Stakeholder validation to discuss, Draft Revised Policy and make further recommendations</narrative>
  </description>
